@startuml
actor User
participant "Next.js Frontend" as Frontend
participant "Next.js API" as Backend
participant "Microsoft Entra ID" as MSAL

User -> Frontend: Clicks "Login"
Frontend -> MSAL: Initiates login flow
MSAL -> User: Prompts for credentials
User -> MSAL: Enters credentials
MSAL -> Frontend: Returns access token
Frontend -> Backend: Makes authenticated API request with token
Backend -> MSAL: Validates token
MSAL -> Backend: Confirms token validity
Backend -> Frontend: Returns API response
@enduml
